    <item>
      <title>福尔肯德对关税的影响，达成新的贸易协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-04-08/faulkender-on-tariffs-impact-reaching-new-trade-deals-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国副财政部长迈克尔·福尔金德（Michael Faulkender）谈到了唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统如何对贸易伙伴征收关税以及如何删除贸易障碍。他还谈到了政府将如何带回制造业和工厂。他在“彭博社近距离”上讲话。 （来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-04-08/faulkender-on-tariffs-impact-reaching-new-trade-deals-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Apr 2025 20:46:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>关税的涡轮增压折叠率降期对冲基金利率下注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-08/diving-swap-spreads-show-violent-conclusion-to-hedge-fund-bet</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的关税的动荡正在加速受欢迎的对冲基金赌注的崩溃，即国债会比利率掉期更好。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-08/diving-swap-spreads-show-violent-conclusion-to-hedge-fund-bet</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Apr 2025 20:34:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>比特币是“重大集会的设置”：Bitwise CIO</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-04-08/bitcoin-is-setup-to-rally-significantly-bitwise-ceo-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普总统对美国贸易伙伴的关税触发了股市比最古老的加密货币比特币更疯狂地摆动。 Bitwise Cio Matt Hougan说，“应该启发比特币公牛”，“如果我们在更广泛的股票市场中获得稳定时期，则可以重大竞争。” （来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-04-08/bitcoin-is-setup-to-rally-significantly-bitwise-ceo-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Apr 2025 18:48:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>PBOC放松抓地力后，中国的海上人民币率低</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-08/pboc-greenlights-yuan-weakness-with-fixing-past-7-2-per-dollar</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在中国对货币的紧密控制之后，海上人民币降到了记录下的最弱水平，美国对许多中国商品的关税104％推向了领先。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-08/pboc-greenlights-yuan-weakness-with-fixing-past-7-2-per-dollar</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Apr 2025 01:19:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
